{"tid":1737491,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"致　呢兩日睇到好撚嬲而又唔敢出街既和理非","createTime":"2019-11-19T03:32:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T05:17:35.000Z","uid":173889,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"88a229835e2aa1857d6675a05572f7fc277cceb3","tid":1737491,"uid":173889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:32:22.000Z","msg":"由尋日出去紅磡救手足既人數可以睇得出<br />\n大部分既和理非都唔敢出去<br />\n亦有少部分升級做初級勇武<br />\n<br />\n請所有呢兩日睇直播睇到好撚嬲而又唔敢出街既和理非<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>請勿放負 勿屌手足 勿被五毛帶風向</strong></span></span><br />\n而家政府就係想你地互相指責，分化<br />\n<br />\n我明白呢兩日大家都好無力好負面<br />\n但係呢場運動係未完！！！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔該大大力轉發文宣，同政府講我地係唔會被分化，永不割席</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">被捕既手足同埋前線需要你地鼓勵，唔好放負！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"555a422f97cdd51fbea8230c887a4ca210e22f49","tid":1737491,"uid":173889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:46:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d6a18d297852ef6bf4b9d329e480d0169ed4130","tid":1737491,"uid":55874,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:59:50.000Z","msg":"真 <br />\n屌還屌 唔好連唔該講嘅都講埋<br />\n指出問題 提出建議 鬧還鬧 留口<br />\n我知道出返嚟嘅手足已經好內疚 而且亦未完全安全<br />\n手足不分離 打下手板好啦"},{"pid":"e0a3be27c12893c92fef1353cb03bac9d988bee6","tid":1737491,"uid":170812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:11:57.000Z","msg":"文宣都好重要!"},{"pid":"46d7ccbc216ab25a054aa7e9c6a49e5f41df72cf","tid":1737491,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:12:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"df2c127edff910cdb02b0a9a15e16232db4a38fd","tid":1737491,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:12:37.000Z","msg":"推！！"},{"pid":"59281410aa662b6f2839b032f53f063